data.description: This lovely Cape Cod property features three bedrooms, two bathrooms & a pristine kitchen with fresh paint & newer appliances. It's situated on a corner lot at the beginning of a cul-de-sac, offering extra privacy. The backyard boasts a beautiful privacy fence & includes a shed with electricity; a private workshop!! Don't forget, there are upcoming installations of a brand new roof and siding, expected to be completed by the end of the year through the insurance company!! Documents showing that a brand new roof and brand new exterior siding is being installed! Too many upgrades to mention -- set up a viewing today!!
